plan (tickers, prices, risk settings) is multi-dimensionally verified by a group of institutional-level specialist AIs. Three personified AIs with advanced expertise in macro correlations, volatility prediction, and order book imbalances sharply critique and review your strategy from their unique perspectives.\",\"form_title\":\"Input Analysis Scenario\",\"form_desc\":\"Please freely enter the outline of the trade you want to verify (entry rationale, expected time horizon, risk tolerance, etc.).\",\"asset_class\":\"Asset Class Selection\",\"fx\":\"Forex (FX)\",\"stocks\":\"Stocks (STOCKS)\",\"crypto\":\"Crypto (CRYPTO)\",\"ticker_selection\":\"Ticker Selection\",\"direction\":\"Direction\",\"buy\":\"Buy\",\"sell\":\"Sell\",\"entry_target\":\"Entry Target\",\"stop_loss_limit\":\"Stop Loss Limit\",\"take_profit_target\":\"Take Profit Target\",\"validate_plan\":\"Verify Plan Validity\",\"loading_1\":\"🌐 Synchronizing macro correlation data...\",\"loading_2\":\"📊 Running order book imbalance protocol...\",\"loading_3\":\"⚖️ Simulating risk governance...\",\"loading_4\":\"💎 Generating premium strategy scenarios...\",\"report_summary\":\"Strategy Verification Report: Summary\",\"plan_label\":\"{ticker} {direction} Plan\",\"overall_eval\":\"Executive Summary: Overall Evaluation\",\"expert_01_title\":\"01 Chief Macro Strategist\",\"expert_01_role\":\"Expertise\",\"expert_01_desc\":\"Major central bank policies, interest rate trends, and global asset correlation deep learning.\",\"expert_02_title\":\"02 Senior Portfolio Manager\",\"expert_02_role\":\"Expertise\",\"expert_02_desc\":\"Financial engineering-based volatility estimation and institutional risk management.\",\"expert_03_title\":\"03 Head of Trading\",\"expert_03_role\":\"Expertise\",\"expert_03_desc\":\"Microstructures, order book imbalances, and sentiment bias execution model.\",\"committee_title\":\"Investment Committee: Strategic Orchestration\",\"consensus_process\":\"Final Consensus Process\",\"agreed_points\":\"Consensus Items\",\"friction_points\":\"Friction Points / Concerns\",\"detailed_report_title\":\"Multi-faceted Market Analysis\",\"final_verdict\":\"Final Verdict on Plan Validity\",\"realtime_metrics\":\"Real-time Metric Scores\",\"macro_fit\":\"Macro Correlation Fit\",\"risk_index\":\"Risk Index\",\"imbalance_index\":\"Order Imbalance\",\"technical_checklist\":\"Technical Checklist\",\"share_report\":\"Share Report\",\"another_plan\":\"Verify Another Plan\",\"disclaimer_title\":\"[Disclaimer]\",\"disclaimer_text\":\"This analysis is a simulation result and does not constitute investment advice. Trading involves risk.\",\"validation_nan\":\"Please enter valid numeric values.\",\"validation_buy_tp\":\"For buy orders, take profit must be higher than entry price.\",\"validation_buy_sl\":\"For buy orders, stop loss must be lower than entry price.\",\"validation_sell_tp\":\"For sell orders, take profit must be lower than entry price.\",\"validation_sell_sl\":\"For sell orders, stop loss must be higher than entry price.\",\"sentiment_label\":\"Social Sentiment Analysis\",\"risk_label\":\"Market Volatility Alert\"},\"track_record\":{\"hero_badge\":\"Honest Performance Disclosure\",\"hero_title\":\"AI Prediction Track Record\",\"hero_desc\":\"Aiming for a world of AI investment without lies. We disclose the raw prediction performance in real time, including all unfavorable results.\",\"total_predictions\":\"Total Predictions\",\"hits\":\"Hits (HIT)\",\"win_rate\":\"Win Rate\",\"pending\":\"Pending\",\"table_date\":\"Date\",\"table_pair\":\"Ticker\",\"table_prediction\":\"Prediction\",\"table_result\":\"Result\",\"up\":\"UP\",\"down\":\"DOWN\",\"hit\":\"HIT\",\"miss\":\"MISS\"},\"pro\":{\"hero_badge\":\"Professional Insights v2.4 Live\",\"hero_title\":\"AI foresees FX market movements.\",\"hero_desc\":\"AI multi-factorially analyzes currency price actions, economic indicators, and market sentiment. Highlighting patterns global traders might miss, directly on your screen.\",\"terminal_title\":\"FX Synapse Terminal\",\"last_sync\":\"Last Sync: {time}\",\"usd_theme_title\":\"USD Market Theme\",\"usd_theme_desc\":\"Expectations of US rate cuts receding. Stronger economic indicators lead to USD strength. Interest rate differentials are the primary driver.\",\"jpy_theme_title\":\"JPY Market Theme\",\"jpy_theme_desc\":\"Seeking exit from negative interest rates. Focus on BoJ policy reversal timing. Key is the virtuous cycle of wages and prices.\",\"sentiment_radar\":\"Market Sentiment Radar\",\"sentiment_bullish\":\"Bullish\",\"sentiment_neutral\":\"Neutral\",\"sentiment_bearish\":\"Bearish\",\"sentiment_desc\":\"Real-time analysis of SNS, news, and options market skews using proprietary AI. Predicting market direction one step ahead of the crowd.\",\"vola_scanner\":\"Volatility Scanner\",\"vola_high\":\"High\",\"vola_mid\":\"Mid\",\"vola_low\":\"Low\",\"vola_desc\":\"Instantly detect volatility anomalies. Capture signs of trend reversals or sudden price shifts by measuring deviations from statistical means.\",\"correlation_matrix\":\"Correlation Assets Matrix\",\"corr_pair\":\"Pair\",\"corr_coeff\":\"Coeff\",\"corr_status\":\"Status\",\"corr_strong_pos\":\"Strong Positive\",\"corr_mid_pos\":\"Moderate Positive\",\"corr_strong_neg\":\"Strong Negative\",\"corr_weak_pos\":\"Weak Positive\",\"corr_desc\":\"Dynamic correlation between major pairs and macro assets (rates, commodities, indices). Determining if current theme is Rates or Risk-Off.\",\"sync_rate\":\"Synapse Sync Rate\",\"consistency_alert\":\"Inconsistency Alert: {level}\",\"view_details\":\"Deep Analysis →\",\"modal_terminal_details\":\"Synapse Terminal Details\",\"current_status\":\"Current Status\",\"sync_consistency\":\"Sync Consistency\",\"mtf_analysis\":\"Multi-Timeframe Analysis\",\"bullish_edge\":\"Bullish Edge\",\"bearish_edge\":\"Bearish Edge\",\"neutral_edge\":\"Neutral\",\"ai_diagnosis\":\"Synapse AI Diagnosis\",\"diagnosis_high\":\"Fewer inconsistencies, expecting price action following technical indicators.\",\"diagnosis_low\":\"Noise detected in some indicators, caution for sudden volatility. AI detects attempts to break resistance.\",\"status_stable\":\"Stable\",\"status_syncing\":\"Syncing\",\"status_in_progress\":\"In Progress\",\"status_divergent\":\"Divergent\",\"cons_high\":\"High\",\"cons_mid\":\"Mid\",\"cons_low\":\"Low\",\"diagnosis_text\":\"The Synapse AI engine has analyzed {pair} with a synchronization rate of {sync}%. The current diagnosis indicates: {detail}\",\"usd_theme_desc_title\":\"US Rate Expectations\",\"jpy_theme_desc_title\":\"BoJ Policy Pivot\"},\"crypto_pro\":{\"hero_badge\":\"Crypto Intelligence v2.4 Live\",\"hero_title\":\"AI thoroughly analyzes the crypto market.\",\"hero_desc\":\"From BTC to SOL, covering everything from major tickers to emerging L1s. AI monitors whale movements and DEX volume to capture the waves of volatility.\",\"terminal_title\":\"Crypto Synapse Terminal\",\"onchain_synced\":\"On-chain Synced\",\"advanced_analysis_layer\":\"Advanced Analysis Layer\",\"market_inter_sync\":\"Inter-market Sync Analysis\",\"btc_vs_us10y_title\":\"BTC vs US 10Y\",\"btc_vs_us10y_desc\":\"BTC's hedge function in a rising rate environment is declining. Correlation as a risk asset is becoming clearer.\",\"onchain_pulse\":\"On-chain Pulse\",\"whale_accumulation_title\":\"Whale Accumulation Status\",\"whale_accumulation_desc\":\"Inflow to major exchanges is decreasing. Whales' transfer to cold wallets is accelerating, suggesting supply shortage.\",\"liquidity_depth\":\"Market Liquidity Depth\",\"depth_range\":\"{range} Depth\",\"bid_side\":\"Bids\",\"ask_side\":\"Asks\",\"liquidity_desc\":\"Integrated analysis of CEX order books in milliseconds. Visualizing 'order book depth' that captures institutional moves and effective slippage during sudden moves.\",\"node_network_pulse\":\"Node Network Pulse\",\"network_load\":\"Network Load\",\"network_stable\":\"Stable\",\"avg_gas_price\":\"Avg Gas Price\",\"node_