hange inflows (sell pressure) and outflows (return to long-term holding).\",\"whale_type_inflow\":\"Inflow\",\"whale_type_outflow\":\"Outflow\",\"whale_type_staking\":\"Staking\",\"whale_target_cold\":\"Cold Wallet\",\"whale_target_protocol\":\"Protocol\",\"modal_crypto_deep\":\"Crypto Synapse Deep Analysis\",\"market_consistency\":\"Market Consistency\",\"onchain_liquidity_matrix\":\"On-chain & Liquidity Matrix\",\"volatility\":\"Volatility\",\"vola_active\":\"Active\",\"vola_stable\":\"Stable\",\"ai_onchain_diagnosis\":\"AI On-chain Diagnosis Report\",\"onchain_high\":\"Low noise, in a region where technical rebound can be expected.\",\"onchain_low\":\"Overall market volatility is rising, caution for sudden slippage is needed.\",\"onchain_diagnosis_text\":\"Currently, {pair} shows a synchronization of {sync}% between on-chain behavior and price action. {detail}\"},\"stocks_pro\":{\"hero_badge\":\"Global Equities Terminal v2.4 Live\",\"hero_title\":\"AI uncovers stock market alpha.\",\"hero_desc\":\"Integrating real-time PER, PBR, and short-term trading signals for S&P 500, Nikkei 225, and major European stocks. The same perspective as institutional investors, right at your fingertips.\",\"terminal_title\":\"Stocks Synapse Terminal\",\"market_data_synced\":\"Market Data Synced\",\"pro_indicators\":\"Pro Indicators\",\"sector_heatmap\":\"Sector Heatmap\",\"earnings_radar\":\"Earnings Radar\",\"ai_momentum\":\"AI Momentum\",\"sector_semi\":\"Semiconductors\",\"sector_tech\":\"Technology\",\"sector_ev\":\"EV / Auto\",\"table_ticker\":\"Ticker\",\"table_date\":\"Date\",\"table_sentiment\":\"AI Sentiment\",\"sent_extreme_bull\":\"Extremely Bullish\",\"sent_neutral\":\"Neutral\",\"sent_caution\":\"Caution Needed\",\"overbought\":\"Overbought\",\"bullish\":\"Bullish\",\"golden_cross\":\"Golden Cross\",\"aligned\":\"Aligned\",\"alpha_scouter\":\"AI Alpha Scouter\",\"bull_divergence\":\"Bull Divergence Continued\",\"bottom_fishing\":\"Bottom Fishing\",\"box_breakout\":\"Box